4. Redistribution of Modified Versions

If you distribute a modified version of the Software, you MUST:

* Include this license file unchanged
* Clearly state that your version is modified
* Credit S44Gaming as the original author
* Provide a visible changelog describing your modifications

Example notice:

"This project is a modified version of software originally created by S44Gaming."

5. No Rebranding

You may not remove references to S44Gaming or present the Software
as if it were entirely your own creation.

Renaming the project is allowed ONLY if the original author attribution
remains clearly visible.

